project.name: OOP-Snap
project.notes: Demonstration of OOP in Scratch (thanks to Brian Harvey). A more extended example of Message Passsing and Inheritance is available ... see "Bringing 'No Ceiling' to Scratch" paper by BH, JM.

block.l: OOP in BYOB? Sure! First, I'll make two counters and say the values of one and think the values of the other. Then I'll pass a message to the Girl to "ask" her to dance.
